<SYNC Start=846111><P Class=KoreanSC>미안해요
<SYNC Start=848111><P Class=KoreanSC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=850735><P Class=KoreanSC>알겠습니다
<SYNC Start=852784><P Class=KoreanSC>&nbsp;
