<SYNC Start=874043><P Class=KoreanSC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=907439><P Class=KoreanSC>응?
<SYNC Start=909439><P Class=KoreanSC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=910975><P Class=KoreanSC>에? 뭐야 이거
